      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Problem Statement 8- A city weather department observed that it rained on 18 out of 30 days in july. Find:\n",
        "1. Probability of rain on a random selected day.\n",
        "2. Probability of no rain on a randomly selected day."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "3qqyE485Bm7c"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "rainy_days=18\n",
        "total_days=30\n",
        "p_rain=rainy_days/total_days\n",
        "p_no_rain=1-p_rain\n",
        "print(\"Weather forecast probability analysis\")\n",
        "print(\"------------------------\")\n",
        "print(\"Total days:\",total_days)\n",
        "print(\"rainy days:\",rainy_days)\n",
        "print(\"\\n Probability of rain=\",p_rain)\n",
        "print(\"Probability of no rain\",p_no_rain)\n",
        "print(\"Percentage chance of rain=\",p_rain*100,'%')\n",
        "print(\"Percentage chance of no rain=\",p_no_rain*100,'%')\n"
      ],
